Class DelayProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.DelayProfile

  • public class DelayProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    A representation of the profile which we will show to the user. We bin the delays into different amounts (we will show as a bar graph/histogram). Used in View and Controller.
